HEADWORD: Eudæmonism
<hw>Eu*d⟦ae⟧"mon*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>
}</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a thinking happy, fr, <?/ blessed
